1
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:49,760
No signs of poisoning

2
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:51,680
No obvious external injuries

3
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:54,000
The cause of death is the same as Shen Qinghai's

4
00:00:54,840 --> 00:00:56,320
Both had their windpipes crushed by great force

5
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,520
And were then hoisted up

6
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:03,520
What is interesting is this red outfit

7
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:06,240
Eye-catching and eerie

8
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,080
It must be a carefully orchestrated setup

9
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:09,480
Meant for the living to see

10
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:11,400
The purpose is to instill fear and terror

11
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:17,040
Fear

12
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:19,720
Shentu Baiqi

13
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:21,800
As a Magistrate

14
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:23,880
You misjudged a case and wronged the innocent

15
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,480
You deserve to die

16
00:01:28,080 --> 00:01:29,000
You deserve to die

17
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:30,760
You deserve to die

18
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:32,080
I understand now

19
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:35,120
Everyone has fear in their heart

20
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:36,320
And this red outfit

21
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:39,160
May be the root cause that triggers the fear in people's hearts

22
00:01:41,360 --> 00:01:42,160
Could it be

23
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,240
That the problem lies with that lamp oil

24
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:46,920
The lamp oil contains hallucinogens

25
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:49,080
Triggering the fear within them

26
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:10,680
No

27
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:15,280
This way, my lords

28
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:20,920
Please do not blame me, my lords

29
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:24,360
I can only lodge you two here for the time being

30
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:25,640
Thank you for your trouble, Village Head

31
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:28,200
Please forgive your humble servant for speaking out of turn

32
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,600
I advise you two to leave as soon as possible

33
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:31,840
You are officials

34
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,080
If something were to happen to you in this township

35
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:37,000
How would your humble servant explain it

36
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,440
You can rest assured about that

37
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:42,400
Whatever happens to us has nothing to do with you

38
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,440
Do not worry too much

39
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:44,680
I have a question

40
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,520
The Method of lighting lamps to repel ghosts

41
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:47,960
Who proposed it

42
00:02:49,320 --> 00:02:49,920
Sun Jia

43
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:54,920
Thank you, Village Head

44
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:55,640
You may go back now

45
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:58,920
Then, my lords, please rest early

46
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,200
If you need anything

47
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,080
My home is not far from here

48
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,760
Summon me at any time

49
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:04,560
By the way, my lords

50
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,720
In this pot is lamp oil

51
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,040
And inside the room

52
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,320
There are oil lamps

53
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:10,680
Be sure not to

54
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:11,680
Extinguish the lamps

55
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,000
Your humble servant takes his leave

56
00:03:24,200 --> 00:03:25,200
Sun Jia

57
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,960
Sun Jia

58
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:32,840
Sun Jia

59
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,760
Sun Jia

60
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:41,000
Who is it in the middle of the night

61
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,160
Who is it

62
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,360
Sun Jia

63
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,200
Who

64
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:13,760
Who is there

65
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,200
Sun Jia

66
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,640
The auspicious hour has arrived

67
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,320
My husband, come back with me

68
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,400
My husband

69
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:55,480
It's a nightmare

70
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:56,760
It's a nightmare, it's a nightmare

71
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,920
I've walked that road since I was a child.

72
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,600
I never expected to meet a ghost that day.

73
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,080
Luckily, I had an oil lamp with me.

74
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:38,480
Otherwise...

75
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,400
So you asked the Village Head...

76
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:41,760
to tell the villagers...

77
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,360
that oil lamps can repel ghosts.

78
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,160
Exactly.

79
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,840
At first, no one believed what I said.

80
00:06:48,440 --> 00:06:50,480
Even I felt I only survived by sheer luck.

81
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:51,800
But then...

82
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,640
more and more people died.

83
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:56,440
If you do not believe me, my lord...

84
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,800
you can go ask Li Laozhang.

85
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,680
He also used the lamp lighting method to repel the ghost...

86
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,360
and survived.

87
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:03,640
Village Head.

88
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:04,840
We found the person.

89
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,160
Dead in the woods.

90
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:07,920
It's all been handled.

91
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:09,280
Handled.

92
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:11,560
Su Qian.

93
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:14,000
I heard from Jia Liang...

94
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:16,160
that you want to leave Wanling Township.

95
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,320
Yes, Village Head.

96
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,880
Leaving aside how scary the ghost is...

97
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,320
just the cost of this lamp oil...

98
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,520
I really can't afford it anymore.

99
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:29,080
I don't dare eat or drink every day.

100
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:32,080
As soon as I have money, I must think of buying this lamp oil.

101
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:33,840
This kind of life...

102
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:35,640
I really don't want to live it anymore.

103
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:38,360
Then regarding the matters of Wanling Township...

104
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:41,360
how can you guarantee you won't speak of them?

105
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:42,720
Rest assured.

106
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,480
What happened back then...

107
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,920
I will take to my grave.

108
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,680
I won't say a word, even in death.

109
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,280
You said it.

110
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,320
You want me to trust you.

111
00:07:56,080 --> 00:07:57,560
I... trust you.

112
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,840
Dump him in the back hills.

113
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,080
Brother.

114
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:22,920
Don't blame your brother for being ruthless.

115
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,640
You broke the rules.

116
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,160
You all saw it.

117
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,720
Su Qian is the example.

118
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:33,280
If any of you want to leave Wanling Township in the future...

119
00:08:33,560 --> 00:08:34,320
don't ever mention it again.

120
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:35,640
Let's go.

121
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:51,600
Li Laozhang.

122
00:08:52,520 --> 00:08:52,960
Li Laozhang.

123
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,040
These two officials...

124
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:57,360
are here to ask you about the situation.

125
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,840
You used the lamp lighting to repel the ghost...

126
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,080
and saved your life.

127
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,000
This life...

128
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:07,760
what difference does it make if it's saved or not?

129
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:11,520
I have no money left to burn lamp oil.

130
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,000
With the last copper coin...

131
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,800
I bought some wine.

132
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,600
Got drunk.

133
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,120
If she comes for me, I won't be afraid.

134
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:21,360
She?

135
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:25,120
That Ghost Bride.

136
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,040
Such a fine young lady.

137
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:29,720
And just...

138
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:32,160
just became a ghost.

139
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:46,800
Poisoned wine

140
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:50,600
My Lord

141
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:52,040
You are indeed here

142
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:54,760
My Lord

143
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:57,400
I must go tell the Village Head of Li Laozhang's death

144
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,880
Take this oil lamp

145
00:09:59,280 --> 00:09:59,800
It's safer this way

146
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:00,560
All right

147
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,360
How is the investigation?

148
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:08,040
The goods lost from Ten Thousand Nations Inn...

149
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:10,360
...have indeed flowed into the markets.

150
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,360
Things are as we guessed;

151
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:13,400
it was indeed an inside job.

152
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:14,560
Furthermore, the sellers

153
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:15,760
are all from Wanling Township.

154
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:19,600
Old Yao,

155
00:10:20,040 --> 00:10:20,280
Hmm?

156
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:21,160
Have you noticed?

157
00:10:21,880 --> 00:10:23,560
Wanling Township has no wealthy families.

158
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,200
Burning lamps all day

159
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:28,400
is truly a considerable expense.

160
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:32,520
And compared to the goods from Ten Thousand Nations Inn?

161
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:34,840
Now that you mention it, I remember.

162
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:36,640
Even the Village Head,

163
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:37,920
his clothing

164
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:39,680
is extremely ordinary.

165
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:43,040
The money gained from robbery,

166
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:44,920
where exactly did it go?

167
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,040
Also,

168
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:49,120
those playing ghosts to rob and those playing to kill,

169
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:50,440
are they the same person?

170
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,000
Then this secret

171
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:58,160
lies with that "her" Li Laozhang mentioned.

172
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,040
There is another matter.

173
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:03,240
On the road to Wanling Township,

174
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:04,600
I found someone dumping a body.

175
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:06,760
Let's go
